</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-eXlEPa iDGZDG pf-45_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-iFMAIt iaxXGt pf-46_ pf-text-1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bUbRBg Gdkwx pf-48_">der Blutdruck,
